data.description: This super clean 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem is nestled in a desirable gated community, offering both security and a sense of community. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by warm-tone tile floors flowing seamlessly throughout the foyer, kitchen, and powder room. The kitchen is the heart of the home making entertaining a breeze, with sleek cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. The open concept brings you into the living spaces, with large sliding glass doors out to the rear patio allowing for lots of natural light. Privacy and tranquility are guaranteed as this townhouse has no backyard neighbors providing a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Upstairs, you'll discover BRAND NEW CARPET, three spacious bedrooms, each offering comfort and relaxation, and the laundry area. The primary bedroom features an ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms are versatile and can be utilized as guest rooms, home offices, ETC. In addition to the townhouse's impressive features, the community amenities are equally enticing like the community pool. This townhouse also offers a one-car garage, providing secure parking and additional storage space as well.
